## ▶️ Running the Pipeline

From a clean R session, run the scripts in order:

```r
source("scripts/01_load_data.R")
source("scripts/02_align_phenology.R")
source("scripts/03_feature_engineering.R")
source("scripts/06_cart_models.R")
source("scripts/08_cart_confusion_matrices.R")
source("scripts/09_plot_cart_trees.R")

After running:
data_clean/ will contain all intermediate and final datasets
figures/ will contain the CART tree diagrams

Dependencies
This project uses:
tidyverse
lubridate
rpart
rpart.plot
caret
Install missing packages with:

install.packages(c("tidyverse", "lubridate", "rpart", "rpart.plot", "caret"))

Reproducibility
This repository is designed so that anyone can clone it and reproduce Objective 1 end‑to‑end.
To test reproducibility:
Clone the repository
Place the raw CSVs into data_raw/
Run the six scripts in order
Confirm that data_clean/ and figures/ populate correctly

